trans-unit.source: Provides a type converter to convert opacity values to and from a string.
trans-unit.target: Gir et typen konverteringsprogram for å konvertere tetthet verdier til og fra en streng.

trans-unit.source: Typically, you do not directly create an instance of an OpacityConverter.
trans-unit.target: Vanligvis du ikke direkte opprette en forekomst av en OpacityConverter.

trans-unit.source: Instead, you call the <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor.GetConverter%2A> method of <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor> class.
trans-unit.target: I stedet kaller du <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor.GetConverter%2A>metoden av <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor>klasse.</xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor> </xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor.GetConverter%2A>

trans-unit.source: For more information about type converters and to view code examples, see the <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeConverter> base class and [How to: Implement a Type Converter](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Du finner mer informasjon om typen konverteringsprogrammer og vise kodeeksempler, kan du se den <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeConverter>basisklasse og [slik: implementere et konverteringsprogram av typen](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).</xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeConverter>

trans-unit.source: Returns a value indicating whether this converter can convert an object of the specified source type to the native type of the converter that uses the specified context.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en verdi som angir om denne konverteringsprogram kan konvertere et objekt av den angitte kildetypen til den opprinnelige typen konverteringsprogram som bruker den angitte konteksten.

trans-unit.source: The `sourceType` is expected to be a <xref:System.String>.
trans-unit.target: Den `sourceType` er forventet å være en <xref:System.String>.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"></xref> that provides information about the context of a type converter.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"> </xref> som gir informasjon om konteksten for en type konverteringsprogram.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Type> that represents the type you want to convert from.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Type>som representerer typen du vil konvertere fra.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if this converter can perform the conversion; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis denne konverteringsprogram kan utføre konverteringen; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Converts the specified object to the converter's native type.
trans-unit.target: Konverterer det angitte objektet til den opprinnelige konverteringstype.

trans-unit.source: The ConvertFrom method is specialized to convert <xref:System.String> values that represent percentages or decimal fractions to their corresponding <xref:System.Double> values, which represent the opacity as a percentage.
trans-unit.target: Metoden ConvertFrom spesialiserte Hvis du vil konvertere <xref:System.String>verdier som representerer prosentdeler eller desimaler til tilhørende <xref:System.Double>verdier, som representerer tettheten i prosent.</xref:System.Double> </xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Types other than <xref:System.String> are passed to the base class implementation of this method.
trans-unit.target: Datatyper enn <xref:System.String>er sendt til basisklasse implementeringen av denne metoden.</xref:System.String>
